sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  participant U as User (Browser)
  participant SPA as Stitch Web App (SPA)
  participant API as Stitch API
  participant DB as DynamoDB (Exports + ACL)
  participant Q as SQS (Export Queue)
  participant W as Lambda (Export Worker)
  participant S3 as S3 (Files + Export Artifacts)
  participant MAIL as Email (SES)
  participant MS as Microsoft Graph (Outlook)

  Note over U,SPA: User clicks Export
  U->>SPA: Open Export modal
  SPA->>API: POST /files/{fileId}/exports
  API->>DB: Check file ACL permission == Collaborator or higher
  alt Allowed
    API->>DB: Create exportJob (Queued)
    API->>Q: Enqueue exportJob
    API-->>SPA: 202 Accepted (exportJobId)
  else Denied
    API-->>SPA: 403 Forbidden
  end

  Q-->>W: Export job message
  W->>DB: Update exportJob status=Running
  W->>S3: GET source file bytes
  W->>W: Render PDF or package artifacts
  W->>S3: PUT export artifact (pdf)

  alt Export as PDF download
    W->>DB: status=Ready + artifactS3Key
  else Export to email
    W->>MAIL: Send email with link or attachment
    W->>DB: status=Sent
  else Export to Outlook
    Note over MS: Requires tenant admin consent\nand per-user OAuth token
    W->>MS: Create draft email or send message
    W->>DB: status=Sent
  end

  SPA->>API: GET /exports/{exportJobId}
  API->>DB: Fetch status + links
  API-->>SPA: 200 OK
  SPA-->>U: Show download or sent confirmation

